author: Brie Stimson
title: Michigan stay-at-home order now bans visits to friends, relatives, governor says
description: Traveling to another home within Michigan, even to visit friends or relatives, or to go to a vacation home, is now banned under Democratic Gov. Gretchen Whitmer’s coronavirus stay-at-home order, which has been extended until May 1.
